rComments: Might've been her first class, but she's just not a good lecturer, and though she does  seem like a nice person and tries to help out people who need help, her way of explaining things is very unclear. The course material itself was pretty hard for me and I feel having her as a prof made it even more difficult than it already was.

I found her teaching style to be very confusing. Had I not already had exposure to proofs from another course, I think I would have done very poorly in her class.   Having said that, help was always available.
This course was hard and material challenging. I found Prof was  patient with questions about explaining difficult concepts. Overall, pretty happy.
